#173

Growing gregariously (locally abundant) on grassy ridgetop surrounded by mixed oak woodland.

- Nearby trees: Black Oak, Ash, Black Walnut, Bur Oak, Honey Locust and distant Northern Red Oak.
- Specimens displayed signs of gravitropism during transport.
